data.title: Moomin Official Site: Discover the Wonders of Moominvalley
data.meta_description: Moomin Official Site: discover Moominvalley and the magical characters created by Tove Jansson. Get the latest Moomin news and stories.
data.text:
Moomin comics debuted in the London Evening News in 1954. This year, D&Q will release a new Moomin comic series in softcover!

Snufkin and Moomintroll, “Snufmin”, have long been a fan favourite. Dive into the journey of this iconic friendship in this article!

Indulge in stories about Tove Jansson’s gay legacy on moomin.com! The Moomin creator was openly gay during times when openness was not easy.

RIMOWA launches a limited-edition capsule collection with Moomin, unveiled at RIMOWA’s pop-up at Isetan department store in Tokyo.

Explore Novita’s popular Moomin knitting patterns and yarns here! In 2022, Novita also published a Moomin-themed knitting book.

Arabia is launching a collection of Moomin home textiles for adults, with bed linen and towels. The collection will come out in the summer of 2023.
